{"tid":196852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓：我們會讓整個美國都遭受災難性後果","createTime":"2017-04-11T14:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T18:37:39.000Z","uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98409afb4f91e0e676eb102cbf516fd29c932ac0","tid":196852,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"［最新消息］<br />\n<br />\nNorth Korea has said it will defend itself &quot;by powerful force of arms&quot; in response to the US deployment of a Navy strike group to the Korean peninsula.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We will hold the US wholly accountable for the catastrophic consequences to be entailed by its outrageous actions,&quot; said the foreign ministry statement quoted by KCNA.<br />\n<br />\n北韓指會以「強力武器」來保衛自己以應對美軍艦隊於朝鮮海峽的部署。<br />\n<br />\n「我們會讓整個美國都遭受災難性後果，來為這些可惡的行動負責。」"},{"pid":"4ec2bb7ba60b9e8d6f2c74a761816c22cc417918","tid":196852,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"很強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e890cb8ff3b60492d56f7a2f0ccd0fc4225669c","tid":196852,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n金仔你唔好縮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b60be9fb2febe03a8b9d150783f8a77fc9348ef","tid":196852,"uid":37297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:38:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>很強硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n把口最硬"},{"pid":"b951bfe5145ee4f9d753427572589c59c10243f5","tid":196852,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:40:26.000Z","msg":"金仔話<br />\n我歡樂組內衣啱啱買架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9205849bd3959e26abe94ef5b4e5f625f14a1d0","tid":196852,"uid":41524,"like":0,"disli